==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Constructively
<hw>Con*struct"ive*ly</hw>, <pos>adv.</pos> <def>In a constructive
manner; by construction or inference.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>A neutral must have notice of a blockade, either actually by a
formal information, or <qex>constructively</qex> by notice to his
government.</q> <rj><qau>Kent.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>constructive-metabolic</ent>⟦br⟧
